txt.en: Speak to Meg Proudfoot in Michel Delving

The Bounders of the Shire need your help.  Return the tokens that you have found to the Bounders in Michel Delving and help Middle-earth protect the bounds of the Shire.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000> NOTE: This quest will be removed from your quest log when Helm's Deep launches. </rgb>

'Thank you for coming to see us.  We are collecting tokens and in return, we will have some special things to offer you once we collect our full bounty.  If you give us five tokens now, we can help complete the Bounty more efficiently.  Then you can come back any time you've collected fifty more tokens.'\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>NOTE: This quest will consume five Bounder's Tokens.</rgb>
